                      "home_domain":  "General / Pluralist",
                      "parent_tool":  "tool10",
                      "general_principle":  "A core design principle stating that an organization\u0027s social systems (team structure, communication) and its technical systems (software architecture, data schemas) should be designed to mirror the same underlying logic. This ensures the organization\u0027s way of working is a living embodiment of the principles it produces."
                  },
