                      "term":  "Stance Sync",
                      "home_domain":  "Business \u0026 Agile",
                      "parent_tool":  "tool4",
                      "general_principle":  "A formal, documented meeting to resolve conflicts between competing priorities (e.g., Design\u0027s \u0027Feel\u0027 vs. Engineering\u0027s \u0027Function\u0027). The Head of Product makes a definitive choice on the primary stance (Learning or Performance) for a specific feature, which then serves as the tie-breaker for all subsequent trade-offs."
                  },
