                                       ],
                      "term":  "Handoff Ritual",
                      "home_domain":  "Business \u0026 Agile",
                      "parent_tool":  "tool5",
                      "general_principle":  "A mandatory meeting at the conclusion of Tool 5 (Structure) where the planning team (e.g., Design, Content) formally presents the final specification to the execution team (e.g., Engineering). The purpose is to transfer tacit knowledge and resolve all ambiguities before execution begins."
                  },
